{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 How to use\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Name your tracks as {\f1 Whatever [X]} where {\b X} is the CC number of each pad (use MIDI monitor to see CC numbers or the example project bundled with this script). Pressing any pad will arm/unarm/mute/unmute the corresponding track.\par}
